      "name": "Fünf Vorteile",
      "settings": {
        "custom_liquid": "<style>.kg-features{background:#FDF8F3;padding:3rem 1.5rem 4rem;border-top:1px solid #F3DED3;}.kg-features__grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(5,1fr);gap:1.5rem;max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto;}@media(max-width:900px){.kg-features__grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);}}@media(max-width:560px){.kg-features__grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);gap:1.25rem;}}.kg-feature{text-align:center;padding:1.5rem 1rem;background:#fff;border-radius:8px;border:1px solid #F3DED3;}.kg-feature svg{color:#CC5740;margin-bottom:.875rem;}.kg-feature__title{font-weight:700;font-size:.9375rem;color:#3D1E14;margin:0 0 .4rem;line-height:1.3;}.kg-feature__text{font-size:.8125rem;color:#7A4535;line-height:1.6;margin:0;}</style><div class=\"kg-features\"><div class=\"kg-features__grid\"><div class=\"kg-feature\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"36\" height=\"36\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path d=\"M9 3H5a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v4m6-6h10a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v4M9 3v18m0 0h10a2 2 0 0 0 2-2v-4M9 21H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-4m0 0h18\"/></svg><p class=\"kg-feature__title\">Ergonomisches Design</p><p class=\"kg-feature__text\">Entwickelt für die natürliche Körperhaltung – rund und geborgen wie im Mutterleib.</p></div><div class=\"kg-feature\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"36\" height=\"36\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path d=\"M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z\"/><polyline points=\"9 12 11 14 15 10\"/></svg><p class=\"kg-feature__title\">Klinisch geprüft</p><p class=\"kg-feature__text\">Unabhängig zertifiziert für maximale Sicherheit – von Experten empfohlen.</p></div><div class=\"kg-feature\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"36\" height=\"36\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path d=\"M20.84 4.61a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 0L12 5.67l-1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 7.78l1.06 1.06L12 21.23l7.78-7.78 1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0 0-7.78z\"/></svg><p class=\"kg-feature__title\">Gesunder Babyschlaf</p><p class=\"kg-feature__text\">Fördert tiefen, erholsamen Schlaf – für euer Baby und euch als Eltern.</p></div><div class=\"kg-feature\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"36\" height=\"36\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path d=\"M12 2a10 10 0 1 0 10 10\"/><path d=\"M12 6v6l4 2\"/></svg><p class=\"kg-feature__title\">Langlebige Qualität</p><p class=\"kg-feature__text\">Hochwertige Materialien, sorgfältig gewählt und auf Langlebigkeit getestet.</p></div><div class=\"kg-feature\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"36\" height=\"36\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"/><line x1=\"2\" y1=\"12\" x2=\"22\" y2=\"12\"/><path d=\"M12 2a15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4-10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4-10z\"/></svg><p class=\"kg-feature__title\">Entwickelt in Deutschland</p><p class=\"kg-feature__text\">Mit Liebe in Berlin nach höchsten deutschen Qualitätsstandards entwickelt.</p></div></div></div>",
